<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Astronomy Picture of the Day</title>
    <style>
        .navbar {
            background-color: #004080;
            padding: 15px;
            color: white;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 100;
            top: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            margin-right: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }


        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding-top: 70px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #004080;
            margin: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #004080;
            text-align: left;
            margin-right: 200px;
            margin-left: 200px;
        }

        form {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffffffcc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: #00000019;
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: 312px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #004080;
        }

        input {
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }


        button {
            background-color: #004080;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #002633;
        }


        img {
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            margin-top: 20px;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        div p {
            text-align: left;
            margin-right: 200px;
            margin-left: 200px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #004080;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="navbar">
    <a href="/astpic">Astronomy Picture</a>
    <a href="/asteroids">Asteroids info</a>
    <a href="/admin">Admin page</a>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/history">History</a>
</div>

<h1>Astronomy Picture of the Day</h1>
<p> The phoro for the day you choose might not open, but the information will be here. <br> Do not choose the date from the future.</p>
<div>
    <form action="/astpic" method="GET">
        <label for="date">Select a date:</label>
        <input type="date" id="date" name="date" required>
        <button type="submit">Get APOD</button>
    </form>
    <h2><%= apodData.title %></h2>
    <p>Date: <%= apodData.date %></p>

    <% if (apodData.date === currentDate) { %>
        <p>This is today's picture!</p>
    <% } %>

    <img src="<%= apodData.url %>" alt="Astronomy Picture of the Day">
    <p><%= apodData.explanation %></p>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>Mitalipova Anida SE-2230</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>